{"tid":2161102,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"「新西蘭」因應疫情推遲大選四周至十月中","createTime":"2020-08-17T11:15:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-17T11:28:54.000Z","uid":219635,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"074ddeaf97e66b8141e2f9ab5e00760e94d7157b","tid":2161102,"uid":219635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T11:15:42.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】新西蘭政府宣布因為新冠病毒疫情，決定推遲原定下月舉行的大選四個星期。<br />\n<br />\n新西蘭經過逾一百天無新增確診個案後，近日疫情出現反彈，周日再多十三人確診，其中十二宗本土感染個案與最大城市奧克蘭的確診病例有關連。當局上周已延長奧克蘭的封城措施十二天。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=401990\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D401990&d=hvnZYtOEdtVTkBm9e3s21Bfhc2i76iEVsdTpjF8%2BTp8%3D&h=f97f5142\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D401990&h=a9eb2920\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=401990</a><br />\n<br />\n而家「五眼聯盟」好多都推遲，又送彈藥比藍屍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n身邊藍屍：屌，人地都推遲啦，係得你班友嘈生晒。<br />\n搞到唔知點答佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d719611477730c5941d4ca5af946ab203c6c4be","tid":2161102,"uid":219635,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T11:16:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cac4f5b1066e19fcf0d630700fa5d6d39ab0b618","tid":2161102,"uid":219635,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T11:16:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21fa2eebca14f45f0bea6aa3401f4126964df9d4","tid":2161102,"uid":219635,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T11:16:28.000Z","msg":"<img sr